Package: diskweaver
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: DiskWeaver Project <noel.phillips@gmail.com>
Depends: mdadm, lvm2, parted, util-linux, e2fsprogs, cockpit-bridge
Description: Storage pooling daemon and Cockpit plugin
 DiskWeaver builds and manages redundant storage pools (mdadm/LVM) from
 arbitrary disks, exposed over a Unix-socket HTTP API and a Cockpit web UI.
 This package installs the diskweaverd daemon (systemd service) and the
 DiskWeaver Cockpit plugin.
